        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 7. Chlorociboria metrosideri (PDD 116740) A fresh apothecia B margin of receptacle in vertical section C surface of receptacle in squash mount showing rough-walled hairs D apex of asci and paraphyses E immature ascus with 8 spores, and mature asci with 4 spores. Scale bars: 0.1 mm (A); 20 µm (B, C); 10 µm (D, E)." ;
